'''GoTrump.com'''（可翻译为'''出发吧特朗普'''<ref name="mg21">{{cite news |title=美国第45届总统：Donald Trump 唐纳德·特朗普（川普）资产及旗下公司 |url=https://www.mg21.com/guide/?p=898 |publisher=美股之家 |access-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622043418/https://www.mg21.com/guide/?p=898 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]在2006年推出的一个{{Le|旅行網站|Travel website}}。该公司后来在2007年关闭。该网站的口号是“旅游交易的艺术”（{{Lang|en|The art of the travel deal}}），引用了特朗普的[[自传|自传]]《[[交易的藝術|交易的艺术]]》。现在，GoTrump.com已经转为一家售卖衣服等日用品的[[网上商城|网上商城]]。

== 历史 ==
2006年1月24日，唐纳德·特朗普在[[纽约|纽约]]的[[特朗普大厦|特朗普大厦]]宣布创建GoTrump.com。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Silverman|first=Stephen M.|title=Trump's Newest Job: Travel Agent|url=http://people.com/celebrity/trumps-newest-job-travel-agent/|accessdate=2017-11-17|work=People|date=2006-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180321194329/http://people.com/celebrity/trumps-newest-job-travel-agent/|archive-date=2018-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>特朗普在新闻发布会上表示：“我会为你找到最好的旅行优惠，不管你是想拥有一个豪华的度假，还是只想在全球的航空公司和酒店享受最优惠的价格。我们已经与[[Travelocity|Travelocity]]、[[美国航空|美国航空]]、[[美国运通|美国运通]]、蓝星喷气机（{{lang|en|Blue Star Jets}}）和Joonbug等知名合作伙伴展开合作。”特朗普投资800亿美元于这个网站中，并建立了他第一个公开的[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]地址：<code>MrTrump@GoTrump.com</code>，以给他人提供旅行建议<ref name="hospi">{{Cite web|title=Donald J. Trump Boards $80 Billion Online Travel Industry with the Launch of GoTrump.com|url=http://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4026024.html|accessdate=2016-03-05|date=2006-01-24|work=hospitalitynet.org|publisher=Hospitality Net|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910144005/http://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4026024.html|archive-date=2016-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特朗普在他的每日广播节目{{Le|Trumped!|Trumped!}}中宣传这个网站，并预计该网站将出现在[[飛黃騰達6|第六季]]的《[[飛黃騰達|飛黃騰達]]》中<ref name="NYT" />。

该网站于2007年关闭。<ref>{{Cite news|title=The Many Business Failures of Donald Trump|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/politics/pictures/the-many-business-failures-of-donald-trump-20110511/trump-magazine-0520002|accessdate=2017-11-26|work=Rolling Stone|date=2011-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019055553/http://www.rollingstone.com/politics/pictures/the-many-business-failures-of-donald-trump-20110511/trump-magazine-0520002|archive-date=2017-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TDB">{{Cite web|title=A Brief History of Donald Trump's Get-Rich Schemes|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/a-brief-history-of-donald-trumps-get-rich-schemes|accessdate=2017-11-26|author=Resnick|date=2016-03-10|first=Gideon|work=The Daily Beast|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319000522/https://www.thedailybeast.com/a-brief-history-of-donald-trumps-get-rich-schemes|archive-date=2018-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>至少从2016年3月起，GoTrump.com这个[[域名|域名]]被[[重定向|重定向]]到DonaldJTrump.com，这是[[2016年唐納·川普競選美國總統|特朗普总统竞选]]的官方网站。<ref name="TDB">{{Cite web|title=A Brief History of Donald Trump's Get-Rich Schemes|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/a-brief-history-of-donald-trumps-get-rich-schemes|accessdate=2017-11-26|author=Resnick|date=2016-03-10|first=Gideon|work=The Daily Beast|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319000522/https://www.thedailybeast.com/a-brief-history-of-donald-trumps-get-rich-schemes|archive-date=2018-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.gotrump.com GoTrump.com → DonaldJTrump.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gotrump.com/ |date=20200602030935 }}. Retrieved November 30, 2017.</ref>现在，GoTrump.com已经转为一家售卖衣服等日用品的[[网上商城|网上商城]]<ref>{{cite web |title=About GoTrump.com |url=https://gotrump.com/pages/about-gotrump-com |publisher=GoTrump.com |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803182249/https://gotrump.com/pages/about-gotrump-com }}</ref>。

== 产品 ==
该网站上推出了6万家酒店<ref name="Wapo">{{Cite news|title=Coming and Going: The Donald Expands|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/01/27/AR2006012700764.html|accessdate=2016-03-05|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2006-01-29|location=[[Washington,_DC|Washington, DC]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301185643/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/01/27/AR2006012700764.html|archive-date=2016-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中包括“特朗普精选”（{{Lang|en|Trump's picks}}），这些酒店宣称是特朗普最喜欢的酒店和度假村<ref name="hospi">{{Cite web|title=Donald J. Trump Boards $80 Billion Online Travel Industry with the Launch of GoTrump.com|url=http://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4026024.html|accessdate=2016-03-05|date=2006-01-24|work=hospitalitynet.org|publisher=Hospitality Net|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910144005/http://www.hospitalitynet.org/news/4026024.html|archive-date=2016-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYT">{{Cite news|author=Tedeschi|first=Bob|title=Now for Sale Online, the Art of the Vacation|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/02/06/technology/now-for-sale-online-the-art-of-the-vacation.html|accessdate=2017-11-26|work=The New York Times|date=2006-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021190854/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/02/06/technology/now-for-sale-online-the-art-of-the-vacation.html|archive-date=2018-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该网站由Travelocity提供支持<ref name="NYDN">{{Cite news|author=Martinez|first=Jose|title=Trump Sez, Come Fly With Me. The Donald's on a Trip With New Travel Website|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/trump-sez-fly-donald-trip-new-travel-web-site-article-1.601721|accessdate=2017-11-26|work=New York Daily News|date=2006-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201031153/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/trump-sez-fly-donald-trip-new-travel-web-site-article-1.601721|archive-date=2017-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这是一家向其他网站提供搜索和预订技术授权的公司。

== 评价 ==
特朗普相信这个网站将会取得“巨大的成功”（{{Lang|en|tremendous success}}）<ref name="NYDN">{{Cite news|author=Martinez|first=Jose|title=Trump Sez, Come Fly With Me. The Donald's on a Trip With New Travel Website|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/trump-sez-fly-donald-trip-new-travel-web-site-article-1.601721|accessdate=2017-11-26|work=New York Daily News|date=2006-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201031153/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/trump-sez-fly-donald-trip-new-travel-web-site-article-1.601721|archive-date=2017-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，{{Le|弗雷斯特研究公司|Forrester Research}}的[[旅游业|旅游行业]]分析师、[[川普航空|川普航空]]前[[营销总监|营销总监]]亨利·哈特韦尔特（{{Lang|en|Henry Harteveldt}}）<ref name="NYT">{{Cite news|author=Tedeschi|first=Bob|title=Now for Sale Online, the Art of the Vacation|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/02/06/technology/now-for-sale-online-the-art-of-the-vacation.html|accessdate=2017-11-26|work=The New York Times|date=2006-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021190854/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/02/06/technology/now-for-sale-online-the-art-of-the-vacation.html|archive-date=2018-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>称GoTrump是特朗普的“[[虚荣|虚荣]]网站”（{{Lang|en|vanity site}}），并表示这个网站赚不了多少钱<ref name="Wapo">{{Cite news|title=Coming and Going: The Donald Expands|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/01/27/AR2006012700764.html|accessdate=2016-03-05|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2006-01-29|location=[[Washington,_DC|Washington, DC]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301185643/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/01/27/AR2006012700764.html|archive-date=2016-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，对特朗普期望不高，认为该网站不会带来每年超过几百万美元的收入<ref name="NYT" />。

